  "text": "Results suggest that inhibition of HIF-1α decreased tumor growth in malignant gliomas [CITATION_1] . Additionally, Dai et al. showed oxygen-independent cytotoxicity and p53-independent apoptosis by HIF-1α inhibition in glioblastoma cells [CITATION_2] . In the present study, Western blot analyses of the cleavage of PARP confirm these findings. Furthermore, treatment of U251MG and U343MG cells with HIF-1α-siRNA or CTM reduced the plating efficiency under normoxic and hypoxic conditions as compared to that of the control siRNA-or DMSO-treated cells.",
